      If your resume isn‚Äôt optimized, it‚Äôs likely never seen by a human recruiter.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li><strong>75%</strong> of resumes are auto-rejected.</li>
      <li><strong>88%</strong> of employers miss top candidates due to poor ATS formatting.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="font-semibold text-red-400">Your skills aren‚Äôt the problem. Your resume format is.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain -->
  <section class="bg-white/5 py-8 sm:py-10 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-md max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6" id="pain">
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-4">üíî The Cost of an Unoptimized Resume</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">You spend hours perfecting your resume, but it never reaches recruiters. Less qualified candidates move ahead while you‚Äôre stuck waiting.</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
      <li>The average job search takes <strong>5‚Äì6 months without ATS optimization</strong>.</li>
      <li>That‚Äôs lost salary, mounting stress, and missed opportunities.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-8 sm:py-12 text-gray-300" id="solution">
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-4 sm:mb-6">The ATS Resume Optimization Solution</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li><strong>Keyword Integration</strong> ‚Äì 85‚Äì90% match from job descriptions</li>
      <li><strong>ATS-Friendly Formatting</strong> ‚Äì recruiter-preferred layouts</li>
      <li><strong>Industry-Specific Language</strong> ‚Äì customized for your role</li>
      <li><strong>Quantified Achievements</strong> ‚Äì impactful bullet points</li>
      <li><strong>Multi-Format Delivery</strong> ‚Äì .docx & PDF included</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Measurable Results -->
  <section class="bg-white/5 py-8 sm:py-12 mt-6 sm:mt-10 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-md max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-gray-300" id="results">
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-4 sm:mb-6 flex items-center">
      Measurable Results You Can Expect
    </h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3">
      <li><strong>Career Growth:</strong> 67% higher interview success rates</li>
      <li><strong>Faster Hiring:</strong> 68% hired within 90 days of using our service</li>
      <li><strong>Higher Earnings:</strong> 7% increase in starting salaries</li>
      <li><strong>Peace of Mind:</strong> Resume guaranteed to pass ATS scans</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose OPTYP -->
  <section class="bg-white/5 py-8 sm:py-12 mt-6 sm:mt-10 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-md max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-gray-300" id="why">
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-4 sm:mb-6 flex items-center">
      Why Choose OPTYP‚Äôs ATS Resume Service?
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
      <div class="hover:bg-white/10 p-4 rounded-lg transition">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Keyword Research</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Analyze 50+ job postings</li>
          <li>Primary + long-tail variations</li>
          <li>Strategic keyword placement</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="hover:bg-white/10 p-4 rounded-lg transition">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Resume Content</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Quantified achievements</li>
          <li>Industry-specific certifications</li>
          <li>Professional summary that sells</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="hover:bg-white/10 p-4 rounded-lg transition">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Technical Optimization</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
          <li>ATS-approved fonts & layouts</li>
          <li>Clean single-column design</li>
          <li>Recognized section headers</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="hover:bg-white/10 p-4 rounded-lg transition">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Our Guarantee</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
          <li>90+ ATS score or free revision</li>
          <li>48‚Äì72 hour delivery (rush available)</li>
          <li>Unlimited revisions for 30 days</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Section -->
  <section id="pricing" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#47C6A2]/20 to-white/10 py-8 sm:py-12 mt-6 sm:mt-10 rounded-xl max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">üí∞ Affordable ATS Resume Pricing</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Invest in your career with a service designed for job seekers.</p>
    <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 max-w-sm mx-auto">
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-2">ATS Resume Optimization</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 line-through text-sm">~‚Çπ599 ($7.99)~</p>
      <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">‚Çπ299 ($3.99)</p>
      <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4">One-time fee. Unlimited revisions for 30 days.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
        <a href="/#contact" 
           class="glass-btn border border-[#47C6A2] w-full sm:w-auto px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_#47C6A2]" 
           aria-label="Get started with ATS resume">
          Get Started
        </a>
        <a href="/faq" 
           class="w-full sm:w-auto px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-white/10 text-sm text-gray-300 hover:text-[#47C6A2] hover:bg-white/5 transition" 
           aria-label="Read FAQ">
          FAQ ‚Üí
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <section class="bg-white/5 py-8 sm:py-12 mt-6 sm:mt-10 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-md max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-4 sm:mb-6">üîó Related Career Services</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-base sm:text-lg">
      <li><a href="/explore/job-portals/linkedin" class="hover:text-[#47C6A2]">LinkedIn Profile Optimization</a></li>
      <li><a href="/explore/job-portals/naukri" class="hover:text-[#47C6A2]">Naukri Profile Optimization</a></li>
      <li><a href="/explore/job-portals/indeed" class="hover:text-[#47C6A2]">Indeed Profile Optimization</a></li>
      <li><a href="/explore/job-portals/github" class="hover:text-[#47C6A2]">GitHub Profile Enhancement</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Final Call to Action -->
  <section id="final-cta" class="text-center py-8 sm:py-12 px-4" aria-labelledby="final-cta-heading">
    <h2 id="final-cta-heading" class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to End Your Job Search Struggles?</h2>
    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-6">
      Join the 67% of professionals landing more interviews with ATS-optimized resumes.  
      <strong>Being qualified isn‚Äôt enough‚Äîyou need to be found.</strong>
    </p>
    <a href="/#contact" 
       class="glass-btn border border-[#47C6A2] block sm:inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-base sm:text-lg transition transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_#47C6A2] mx-auto"
       aria-label="Get Started Today">
      Get Started Today
    </a>

    <ul class="mt-6 text-gray-400 text-sm space-y-1 max-w-md mx-auto text-left sm:text-center" aria-hidden="false">
      <li>‚úì 90+ ATS Compatibility Score Guaranteed</li>
      <li>‚úì 48-Hour Professional Delivery</li>
      <li>‚úì Unlimited Revisions for 30 Days</li>
      <li>‚úì Industry-Certified Resume Writers</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Like & Share -->
  <section class="text-center py-8 sm:py-10">
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Was this page helpful?</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-3" role="status" aria-live="polite">
      <button id="like-yes" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#47C6A2]/20" aria-pressed="false">üëç Yes</button>
      <button id="like-no" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-400/20" aria-pressed="false">üëé No</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Floating sticky CTA (added to prevent JS errors and to keep same UX) -->
  <a id="sticky-cta" href="/#contact"
     class="fixed right-6 bottom-6 z-50 rounded-2xl p-3 px-4 backdrop-blur bg-white/8 border border-white/10 shadow-lg flex items-center gap-3 transform transition hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
     aria-label="Get started (sticky)">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"/></svg>
    <span class="font-medium">Get started</span>
  </a>

  <!-- JSON-LD: Service + Offer (helps rich results) -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Service",
      "serviceType": "ATS Resume Optimization",
      "name": "ATS Resume Optimization Service",
      "description": "Make your resume pass ATS filters and land more interviews with keyword-rich, recruiter-friendly resumes.",
      "provider": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "OPTYP",
        "url": "<?= " + JSON.stringify(Astro.site?.origin || "") + " ?>"
      },
      "areaServed": "IN",
      "offers": {
        "@type": "Offer",
        "url": "<?= " + JSON.stringify(canonicalUrl) + " ?>",
        "priceCurrency": "INR",
        "price": "<?= " + JSON.stringify(String(priceNumeric)) + " ?>",
        "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock"
      }
    }
  </script>

  <script>
    // Like feedback (keeps your original behavior, with small accessibility tweaks)
    document.getElementById('like-yes')?.addEventListener('click', function() {
      this.textContent = 'Thanks! üëç';
      this.classList.add('bg-[#47C6A2]/20');
      this.setAttribute('aria-pressed', 'true');
    });
    document.getElementById('like-no')?.addEventListener('click', function() {
      this.textContent = 'Thanks for feedback';
      this.classList.add('bg-red-400/20');
      this.setAttribute('aria-pressed', 'true');
    });

    // Sticky CTA hide when final CTA visible (safe guards added)
    const stickyCTA = document.getElementById("sticky-cta");
    const finalCTA = document.getElementById("final-cta");

    function checkCTA() {
      if (!stickyCTA || !finalCTA) return;
      const rect = finalCTA.getBoundingClientRect();
      if (rect.top < window.innerHeight && rect.bottom >= 0) {
        stickyCTA.classList.add("translate-y-full");
      } else {
        stickyCTA.classList.remove("translate-y-full");
      }
    }

    document.addEventListener("scroll", checkCTA, { passive: true });
    window.addEventListener("resize", checkCTA);
    window.addEventListener("load", checkCTA);
  </script>

</Layout>
